4️⃣ Understanding Repository Design
This repository follows Kustomize architecture.
Two main parts exist:
Base
Common configuration for all environments.
base/
Contains:
Component	Purpose
database	database resources
exoplanets	web application
________________________________________
Overlay
Environment-specific configuration.
overlays/production
Overlay modifies base resources.
Example:
•	production uses more replicas
________________________________________
5️⃣ Examine Base Kustomization
File:
base/kustomization.yaml
Content:
kind: Kustomization
resources:
- database
- exoplanets
Explanation
This file tells Kustomize:
Use resources from:
base/database
base/exoplanets
Kustomize merges them into a single deployment manifest set.
