8️⃣ Deploy Application Using Kustomize
Command
oc apply -k base
Explanation
Option	Meaning
apply	create or update resources
-k	apply Kustomize directory
Kustomize performs:
1.	reads kustomization.yaml
2.	collects all resource YAML files
3.	merges them
4.	sends final manifests to Kubernetes API
