1️⃣4️⃣ Examine Production Overlay
Directory:
overlays/production
Files:
kustomization.yaml
patch-replicas.yaml
________________________________________
Overlay kustomization.yaml
File:
overlays/production/kustomization.yaml
Content:
kind: Kustomization
resources:
- ../../base/

patches:
- path: patch-replicas.yaml
  target:
    kind: Deployment
    name: exoplanets
Meaning
Overlay:
1.	loads base configuration
2.	applies a patch
________________________________________
Patch File
patch-replicas.yaml
Content:
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: exoplanets
spec:
  replicas: 2
Effect
This modifies the deployment:
replicas: 1
→
replicas: 2
Why?
Production needs higher availability and scalability.
