Real Production Workflow
In real companies the workflow looks like this:
Git repository
     ↓
Base Kubernetes manifests
     ↓
Environment overlays
     ↓
CI/CD pipeline
     ↓
OpenShift cluster deployment
This approach enables:
•	GitOps
•	environment consistency
•	automated updates
•	scalable deployment

